ill start producing it. This is done out of self interest, but it also benefits society. As a whole it will make the gods available to more people as well as lowering the price again.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:endParaRPr lang="zh-CN" altLang="en-US" dirty="0"/></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp></p:spTree></p:cSld><p:clrMapOvr><a:masterClrMapping/></p:clrMapOvr></p:sld>